Hero: These inscriptions... they speak of a "Six-Stat Balance."
Guide: Grit and Flow, Gusto and Focus, Shine and Shade. To master one is to be strong; to master all is to be truly free.
Hero: And the weather?
Guide: The world reflects your spirit. When you are restless, the winds howl. When you are still, the frost bites.
=> END
